    <skos:editorialNote>This file contains the 200811 version of CGI Determination methods vocabulary. Methods of measuring orientation of geometrical features in rock bodies. Describes the way the dip value was determined e.g. measured, inferred from dip slope etc.</skos:editorialNote>
