    <skos:inScheme rdf:resource="urn:cgi:classifierScheme:CGI:DeterminationMethod_orientation:200811" />
    <skos:definition>Orientation of a geologic structure based on observation from a distance great enough to preclude direct inspection of the structure to determine orientation.</skos:definition>
